By cheap I meant Deemos crawling to Surge before I could reply. Its no big 
deal, though, we can forget about it.

I'm off to catch up on sleep in a few mins. C ya all tomorrow.

::Oblitertron/Zardus/Reptilica/Breakdown::

Oblitertron stops, nearly stepping on Deemos as the bot gives his offer. He 
roars in rage when Serge runs off, running off after him and firing.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zardus follows after Oblitertron, Breakdown and Reptilica swooping down 
toward Diskus.
